{"tid":1019083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府擬容許個案方式處理移交逃犯　民主黨憂會被濫用","createTime":"2019-02-12T16:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T16:42:15.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa07cf05b8f4f2fe1c9954596a2b359d34259428","tid":1019083,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442505-20190212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442505-20190212.htm&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=2261ee64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442505-20190212.htm&h=683e442c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442505-20190212.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局建議修例，容許香港與未訂有移交逃犯長期安排的地方，以一次性個案方式處理，透過行政長官發出證明書，提供基礎以啟動處理臨時拘捕及移交的請求，法庭會仔細審核，確保符合法例規定及人權保障。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯支持修例，但民主黨擔心修例後，移交逃犯會被濫用。"}]}